command line
  :source % -> source current file

  :noh -> remove highlights

  :vs -> vertical split    // :vs <filename> , skips :e 
  :sp -> horizontal split  // :sp <filename> , skips :e

normal mode
  J -> Appends next line to current line

  zz -> centres cursor vertically

  gcc -> toggle commment on current line
  gc -> toggle comment motion

  gd -> go to definition of text under cursor 

  <C-o> -> jump back 
  <C-i> -> jump forward

visual mode
  gc -> toggle commont selected region

