  normal mode
    <C-d> -> move down with cursor centered
    <C-u> -> move up with cursor centered

    n -> centres next word (during search)
    N -> centres previous word (during search)

    <leader>f -> format code

    x -> delete no yank

    <leader>s -> replace word cursor is on globally

    <leader>x -> makes file executable
    
    <leader>to -> open new tab
    <leader>tx -> close current tab
    <leader>tn -> go to next tab
    <leader>tp -> go to prev tab
    <leader>tf -> open curr tab in new tab
    <leader>t1/2/3/4..9 -> go to ith tab
    
    <C-h/j/k/l> -> navigation between splits
    <C-arrow keys>+ -> splits resize
    <leader>s= -> equalize split
    <leader>sv -> vertical split
    <leader>sh -> horizontal split
    <leader>sx -> close split
    <leader>so -> close all but this split
    <leader>sm -> split maximize/ minimize split

    <leader>fp -> yank current file path

    - -> open oil in parent directory, go up parent directory in oil
    <leader>- -> open oil in floating window
    <C-p> -> preview file in oil
    <C-l> -> refresh current directory in oil
    oil window
      g. -> toggle show hidden file
      g? -> oil useful commands

    <leader>lg -> open lazygit

